== 批评 ==
一些分析师认为，小额信贷可以给社区带来无法逃避的负债。<ref>{{cite news |last=Sharma |first=Sudhirendar |date=2002-09-25 |title=Is micro-credit a macro trap? |url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.in/2002/09/25/stories/2002092500810900.htm |work=The Hindu Business Line |accessdate=2006-12-02 |archive-date=2013-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130528121612/http://www.thehindubusinessline.in/2002/09/25/stories/2002092500810900.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Sharma |first=Sudhirendar |date=2002-01-05 |title=Microcredit: Globalisation unlimited |url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.in/2002/01/05/stories/2002010500111200.htm |work=The Hindu |accessdate=2006-12-02 |archive-date=2013-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130528121203/http://www.thehindubusinessline.in/2002/01/05/stories/2002010500111200.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=[[France_24|France 24]] |date=2008-04-06 |title=The crushing burden of microcredit |url=http://www.france24.com/en/20080404-bangladesh-burden-microcredit-caring-grameen-bank-mohammed-yunnus |publisher=[[France_24|France 24]] |accessdate=2011-04-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110315142122/http://www.france24.com/en/20080404-bangladesh-burden-microcredit-caring-grameen-bank-mohammed-yunnus |archivedate=2011-03-15 }}</ref> 研究人员发现，格莱珉银行提供的贷款造成贫困的家庭为了偿还贷款，不得不出售他们的财产，甚至造成极端情况下因为压力和屈辱而自杀。<ref>{{cite web |title=Mikrolånen har blivit en skuldfälla för fattiga (Swedish) |url=http://svt.se/2.151554/1.2329694/mikrolanen_har_blivit_en_skuldfalla_for_fattiga |publisher=SVT.se |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110225110607/http://svt.se/2.151554/1.2329694/mikrolanen_har_blivit_en_skuldfalla_for_fattiga |archivedate=2011-02-25 |access-date=2018-02-19 }}</ref>

[[米塞斯研究所|米塞斯研究所]]的Jeffrey Tucker建议小额信贷银行应依靠补贴经营，从而成为福利的另一种形式。<ref>{{cite web |authorlink=Jeffrey Tucker |last=Tucker |first=Jeffrey |title=The Micro-Credit Cult. ''The Free Market'' |publisher=[[Mises_Institute|Mises Institute]] |date=November 1995 |url=https://mises.org/freemarket_detail.aspx?control=215 |accessdate=2018-02-19 |archive-date=2014-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140724130611/http://mises.org/freemarket_detail.aspx?control=215 |dead-url=no }}</ref>尤努斯认为他不走传统的补贴经营路线，给借贷者自食其力创造商机的机会。Tucker基于对于“16项宗旨”的理解对尤努斯提出了批评，他认为这16项宗旨是一种在不了解贫穷、文盲的农民的前提下的一种盲目灌输。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mises.org/library/microcredit-or-macrowelfare-myth-grameen|title=Microcredit or Macrowelfare: The Myth of Grameen|first=|last=anne|date=2006-11-03|publisher=|accessdate=2016-06-16|archive-date=2018-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180906011411/https://mises.org/library/microcredit-or-macrowelfare-myth-grameen|dead-url=no}}</ref>Maulana Ibrahim，孟加拉的一位[[阿訇|阿訇]]，以格莱珉银行在促进非伊斯兰生活方式为由批评了格莱珉银行。他声称，银行要求女性不再服从自己的丈夫，不再忍受贫困的生活。<ref>{{Cite journal | url = https://books.google.com/?id=YS_FlaACPgMC&pg=PA119&lpg=PA119&dq=grameen+bank+against+men#v=onepage&q=grameen%20bank%20against%20men&f=false | title = Women and Islam in Bangladesh: Beyond subjection and tyranny | isbn = 978-0-312-22219-2 | author1 = Hashmi | first1 = Taj ul-Islam | year = 2000}}</ref>

挪威的纪录片《陷入微债务》中指控，格莱珉银行存在逃税问题，西班牙纪录片《小额信贷》也表明了这一观点。该指控是基于-{}-格莱珉银行在1996年，在免税期前非法将约1亿美元的挪威发展合作署（NORAD）的捐款，从一个格莱珉实体转移到了另一个的格莱珉银行。然而，NORAD在2010年12月发表声明，澄清尤努斯及格莱珉银行不存在任何不当行为，并附上了由国际发展署委托的NORAD的捐赠的综合评估。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.regjeringen.no/en/aktuelt/report_grameen/id627366/|title=Report on Norwegian assistance to Grameen Bank|last=Affairs|first=Ministry of Foreign|date=2010-12-07|website=Government.no|language=en-GB|access-date=2017-04-18|archive-date=2018-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180124005729/https://www.regjeringen.no/en/aktuelt/report_grameen/id627366/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

尤努斯否认这是逃税行为：
<blockquote>
不存在逃税的问题。政府为组织提供了机会，我们利用这些机会来帮助我们的股东，孟加拉农村贫穷妇女。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.muhammadyunus.org/In-the-Media/a-full-transcript-from-the-press-conference-held-on-december-12-2010/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2018-02-19 |archive-date=2012-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120218002413/http://www.muhammadyunus.org/In-the-Media/a-full-transcript-from-the-press-conference-held-on-december-12-2010/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref></blockquote>

David Roodman <ref>{{cite web |url=http://cgdev.org/content/expert/detail/2719/ |title=David Roodman : Center for Global Development : CGD Experts |date=2009-10-22 |publisher=Cgdev.org |accessdate=2009-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051220132652/http://www.cgdev.org/content/expert/detail/2719/ |archive-date=2005-12-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>和Jonathan Morduch <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nyu.edu/projects/morduch/ |title=Jonathan Morduch's Home Page |publisher=Nyu.edu |accessdate=2009-12-20 |archive-date=2016-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826211040/http://www.nyu.edu/projects/morduch/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>基于情况的复杂性，对小额信贷对贫困作用的研究在统计意义上的有效性提出了质疑。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.cgdev.org/open_book/2009/06/roodman-morduch-2009.php |title=New Challenge to Studies Saying Microcredit Cuts Poverty | David Roodman's Microfinance Open Book Blog |publisher=Blogs.cgdev.org |accessdate=2009-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130313231645/http://blogs.cgdev.org/open_book/2009/06/roodman-morduch-2009.php |archive-date=2013-03-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> Yoolim Lee和Ruth David发现在印度南部，小额信贷和格莱珉模式正在被风险投资和对利润的追逐所扭曲。在某些情况下，贫穷的农村家庭遭受了债务螺旋，小额融资讨债者的骚扰，有时甚至是自杀。

